{"tid":1559910,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"無懼藍絲！跳閘被捕經驗分享暨圍爐區","createTime":"2019-09-11T04:16:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T10:36:32.000Z","uid":31317,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"fde7f84f5b2dd09ad5bd64e7b67631b65a4bc714","tid":1559910,"uid":31317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:16:33.000Z","msg":"話說我朋友因為以為有港鐵跳閘優惠Jump咗，<br />\n於是被藍絲周到，不過本住唔撚驚嘅心冇撚跑走到仲大大聲同佢理論（我知都somehow on9），有少少心得想同大家分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（TLDR可以睇最底）<br />\n<br />\n<ins>事發經過</ins><br />\n我朋友係女仔，<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">（因為以為港鐵有跳閘優惠）</span></span>跳咗入閘，<br />\n跳時睇過閘位冇狗、職員、便便、粉人、黃人、藍絲，<br />\nJump完後兩秒無啦啦有隻藍絲後面追住我朋友話做咩跳閘，<br />\n（應該係喺朋友後面入閘，唔係突登捕）<br />\n然後就<strong>推我朋友行咗幾步佢想擋我朋友走</strong>，話做咩唔比錢入閘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n我朋友話冇喎果啲啦，佢話你快啲返去比錢唔係報警，<br />\n我朋友話你咪報囉，你而家非禮我，有其他人睇到，<br />\n然後其他善心嘅路人就開始圍觀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n跟住佢就開始打電話畀毅進仔，我朋友就<strong>行返去拍卡</strong>，<br />\n當中MTR職員都有查詢<del>提示</del>我朋友係咪已經畀返錢拍咗卡，<br />\n拍左卡咁起碼已經冇得罰我朋友錢，佢個報警都作廢（at least唔係刑事）；<br />\n然後成班人圍佢同佢<del>嘈</del>理論，好多手足一齊參與呢個討論大會，<br />\n仲有好幾位女士非常勇敢，超大聲字字鏗鏘，我朋友表示非常感謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPOPO打返比佢問佢settle未，佢話我朋友已經比左錢但成班人圍緊佢，<br />\n因為朋友已畀錢，佢就同我朋友講話可以唔追究，<br />\n（其實港鐵職員都出哂黎冇一個話要追究）；<br />\n我朋友就撚唔爽大聲講：「而家唔係你唔追，而家我要追究你非禮呀」<br />\n咁就照叫popo黎，因為朋友<strong>考慮過</strong>而家係佢理虧<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後popo黎左，有隻母狗語氣勁惡劣一開始，<br />\n咁寫完一輪留左身份證，話mark低不追究咁，又話要電話地址，<br />\n我朋友就<strong>好堅持</strong>，既然而家我暫時唔追究，點解仲要電話地址？<br />\n母狗就話總之而家個程序要你比，<br />\n另外一個較冷靜popo又話其實我朋友有權唔比都得，我朋友話咁我唔比，<br />\n然後等MTR張warning letter時，我朋友就開始分化佢地good cop bad cop<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我朋友對住母狗講：「呀PCXXXXXX吓嘛（同時用手機mark低佢number），<br />\n你地警察其實除左投訴有冇得讚賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？」<br />\n母狗聽到自己number ＋ 讚賞呢啲180度大轉變，<br />\n話：「乜你會想讚嫁咩」、「如果多啲人讚就好」<br />\n我朋友內心be like: <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我朋友話：「咁你做得好就會讚 做唔好比人彈好合理姐」<br />\n然後佢開始精神分裂扮好人，話：<br />\n「果邊有人影你喎 你洗唔洗過去同佢講聲 地鐵範圍唔知乜乜乜喎」<br />\n我朋友話：「都叫冇肖像權嫁啦我又冇做啲咩咪由佢影」<br />\n佢就話即係我想同你講你有咁既權利姐blahblahblah<br />\n<br />\n然後收MTR warning，MTR職員同母狗重申我朋友可以喺閘口處理，<br />\n唔需要入站長室（even母狗有扮好人話想保障我朋友私隱），<br />\nMTR職員都拎左張form出嚟話可以喺閘口填，唔需要入站長室<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<br />\n填完就了事，冇罰款<br />\n<br />\n之後好多同善良的路人陪我走，<br />\n亦有人主動留電話話如果之後要告嘅話可以搵佢幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有兩個以為我比人罰錢想比錢我，話：<br />\n「攞住啦 攞完下次先有得再跳嫁嘛」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過因為我冇被罰錢，所以就叫佢哋留返畀小朋友<br />\n<br />\n<ins>事後檢討</ins><br />\n1. 我朋友都係一半好彩，先冇比人不合理對待：<br />\n藍絲有郁手有理虧、有好多好多同路人幫、MTR職員不追究、狗仔唔太惡而我朋友亦唔太驚<br />\n2. Jump前要評估環境（除左前面睇埋後面，多緊貼跳閘消息）<br />\n3. 同路人一定一定一定一定要幫手，我朋友係路人度得到好多支援，<br />\n無論係屌藍絲定提供意見定個人冇咁驚（例如話呢d係港鐵附例唔係刑事blahblahblah）<br />\n4. 據理力爭前留意自己有咩「渣拿」，我朋友嘅情況係即使佢被抄牌最多都係罰$500，對我嚟講afford到就ok，如果之前比人抄過／有其他事就真係要快閃<br />\n5. 同Popo一定要據理力爭，唔明嘅嘢問到明，你有權唔入站長室（如MTR職員OK）、你有權唔留電話地址、你有權問Popo每做一樣野係咩目的<br />\n6. 對住popo一定要大聲朗讀並抄低號碼，畀佢知道邊個係主人邊個係狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下開放討論、經驗分享及圍爐取暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d365f6021f03294ad3127e5a6b5c5f3a1c79a3b8","tid":1559910,"uid":4519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:19:50.000Z","msg":"我覺得睇站，係個職員放生你姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b313b77d5472fcf6e90d932e3b13783c319590","tid":1559910,"uid":20283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:19:53.000Z","msg":"915呀 又冇人講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1559911\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1559911</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ab5bf294d754a76d8eacfded0796e6a147c71044","tid":1559910,"uid":31317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:19:57.000Z","msg":"推1"},{"pid":"8667c4bdcf461ae20c47f252bf53181f474763c3","tid":1559910,"uid":31317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d365f6021f03294ad3127e5a6b5c5f3a1c79a3b8","tid":1559910,"uid":4519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:19:50.000Z","msg":"我覺得睇站，係個職員放生你姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:21:06.000Z","msg":"呢個真，我都聽好多係走唔到，<br />\n所以我其中一點conclusion係要睇自己當時有咩「渣拿」<br />\n當時藍絲話唔追究就可以走其實，但好撚不爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"021d4ac994e186e29877a8bfdef23748b5283434","tid":1559910,"uid":213978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:23:01.000Z","msg":"做得好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8652c7e0886474aa7e5f2173c29fc53f4100b6","tid":1559910,"uid":213978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:23:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做得好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"fd515a3b3c1d9121117521a465d90b29abcef215","tid":1559910,"uid":54373,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://j.gifs.com/OMqVlB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fj.gifs.com%2FOMqVlB.gif&h=faee4a7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5PLAJmA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5PLAJmA.jpg&h=906da6c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9d13350cbc5e9227df6b3b2bf0744f5d6201fb0a","tid":1559910,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:29:21.000Z","msg":"入閘買最平單程飛，出跟人出或 跳走<br />\n入 閘 後捉到你機會大"},{"pid":"8a6573ee5f364c7e7bf07a01a70ac429dab15f86","tid":1559910,"uid":64830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:29:40.000Z","msg":"721唔見人 831打死人 915銅鑼灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6715cfc1115f1ba6ad06ab1b146a46a16d7f740b","tid":1559910,"uid":196459,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:35:09.000Z","msg":"你朋友好叻女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4be950861a5b873e1c7f8b6eb9e4c362a21a1531","tid":1559910,"uid":31317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bc8652c7e0886474aa7e5f2173c29fc53f4100b6","tid":1559910,"uid":213978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T04:23:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做得好<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:18:09.000Z","msg":"呢個真係好撚想笑，我朋友冇突登撚，<br />\n但估唔到對讚賞咁有渴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d728fc67e720b02ba869c54242d6f94bf1bf329","tid":1559910,"uid":60398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T05:54:11.000Z","msg":"幫推<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>未爛未拆 咁樣入！</strong></span></span><br />\n[制裁黨鐵] 低調跳閘方法 必定通關<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1524993\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1524993</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QG5GZ57.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQG5GZ57.gif&h=70f70c88&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmZ8JRV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmZ8JRV.gif&h=d48b36ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xQ6rr7H.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxQ6rr7H.gif&h=2e882f27&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ch4X7sO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fch4X7sO.jpg&h=971c9013&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少八達通<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點吶喊！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests #Chinazi<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=3A5iQKMTOMHlOvaIjHeRepq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=6ef44cb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著copy and paste呢段嘢<br />\n6. 保持獨立思考，分析能力level up，抵抗fake news/ rumour <br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 做孝子救港，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.06"},{"pid":"e6dccf79d6d14e6f7e185e642de04c6d58650435","tid":1559910,"uid":31317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:17:58.000Z","msg":"又到放工時間，輕輕一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84b0fcd0a608652fdfb8435c0274fb8b7643a317","tid":1559910,"uid":188805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:36:32.000Z","msg":"一開波都係跳閘多<br />\n但之後解鎖咗跟閘功能就有如行雲流水<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw之前有次跳完閘有個藍絲話我無錢唔好搭，我理都無理繼續行，佢自己一路行一路鬧激到好似就快爆血管咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：做開gym"}]}